Subset of Tuberculosis data

Source: R/data.R
tb_clean.Rd

See references for more details. The data is collected between 2003-2009 in Maryland, USA. This is originally from xie2018InfectionTrees

tb_clean

Format

The object is a data frame of dimension 1137x10. Each row is a detected case of TB.

sex

Sex of individual (F/M/Unknown)

county

county in MD

ageatrept

age of individual

race

race of individual (Asian/Black or African American/White)

spsmear

Smear status of individual (positive/negative/unknown)

hivstatus

HIV status of individual (positive/negative/unknown)

homeless

Homelessness status of individual (yes/no)

INIT_REGIMEN_START_DATE

date of start of treatment

PCR.Cluster

Cluster group (if any)

datecoll

Date sputum was collected
